items.name: FlexFit Resistance Bands
items.description: FlexFit Resistance Bands come in a set of five varying resistance levels, perfect for a wide range of exercises. These high-quality, snap-resistant bands are made from natural latex and are ideal for strength training and physical therapy.

items.name: EndurancePro Treadmill
items.description: The EndurancePro Treadmill is built for serious runners and fitness enthusiasts. Featuring a powerful 3.5 HP motor, a large 20” x 60” running surface, and an advanced shock absorption system, this treadmill ensures a smooth and comfortable run.
